name: UDataRegistry
doc: Defines a place to efficiently store and retrieve structure data, can be used as a wrapper around Data/Curve Tables or extended with other sources

RegistryType: Globally unique name used to identify this registry
IdFormat: Rules for specifying valid item Ids, if default than any name can be used
ItemStruct: Structure type of all for items in this registry
DataSources: List of data sources to search for items
TimerUpdateFrequency: How often to check for cache updates
